Yésica Toscanini (Spanish pronunciation: [ˈʝesika toskaˈnini]; born 26 March 1986 in Junín, Argentina)[1] is a professional Argentine fashion model.

She appeared in the 2006 and 2007 Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issues.[2][3] She was photographed for the cover of the Argentine edition of Cosmopolitan and twice for Para Ti magazine. She also appeared in the Abercrombie & Fitch catalog of 2006. She played the high school sweetheart of Enrique Iglesias in the music video for "Do You Know? (The Ping Pong Song)".[4] In 2008 she was selected as the girl for the Intimissimi spring–summer ad campaign.[1]

Through legal counsel she requested, and was granted the right, to have all her images and data to be removed from internet search results in Argentina.[5]
